%h1 TA Sign Ups

%p
  Hello #{@ta['name']}! I hope you're doing well! This is your friendly monthly reminder to sign up to TA for Girl Develop It Chicago classes.

%p
  %b Remember!
  You're elligible to receive credit hours toward upcoming Girl Develop It Chicago courses.

%p
  Additional course information is below, and can also be found on your private sign up page.

%p.center
  %a.button{href: "http://gdichicago.herokuapp.com/teaching_assistants/#{@ta['private_id']}"}
    View private sign up page
  %br
  %br
  %span.small
    Or copy this link into your browser:
    %br
    %a{href: "http://gdichicago.herokuapp.com/teaching_assistants/#{@ta['private_id']}"}
      http://gdichicago.herokuapp.com/teaching_assistants/#{@ta['private_id']}

%h2 Credit hour balance

%p
  %b Balance:
  = @ta['balance'] || 0

%p
  %b Pending balance:
  = @ta['pending_balance']
  %br
  .small Your pending balance includes classes you have signed up to TA that haven't happened yet.

%h2 Upcoming Courses

%p For additional information about the course, click the course name. You will be taken to the Meetup page.

- @courses.each do |course|
  %p
    %h4= link_to course['name'], course['url']
    = course['date']
    at
    = course['location']

